'''萨塞克斯路24号'''（{{lang-en|24 Sussex Drive}}；{{lang-fr|24, promenade Sussex}}。原称Gorffwysfa，是[[威尔士语|威尔士语]]“休憩之地”或“安息所”之意）是[[加拿大总理|加拿大总理]]的官邸，位于[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略省|安大略省]][[渥太华|渥太华]]的[[萨塞克斯路|萨塞克斯路]]上。

== 使用 ==
不同于[[唐寧街10號|唐寧街10號]]或[[白宫|白宫]]，萨塞克斯路24号只作为总理的住所，而总理的办公地点在[[國會山莊_(加拿大)|国会山庄]]旁的{{le|总理和枢密院办公室|Office of the Prime Minister and Privy Council}}大楼内。

由于房屋状况不佳，幼年曾住在这里的[[賈斯汀·杜魯多|賈斯汀·杜魯多]]在2015年自己成为总理后没有迁入，并表示在整个总理任期内都不会回到这里<ref>{{cite news |last1=Tunney |first1=Catharine |title=Trudeau says he doesn't see himself ever returning to live at 24 Sussex |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/24-sussex-drive-trudeau-not-living-1.4511732 |accessdate=2019-05-21 |work=CBC News |date=2018-02-01}}</ref>。

== 建筑 ==
1950年该屋曾翻新过一次，此后就很少有对其的维护花费，导致房内部件逐渐耗损和过时<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://torontosun.com/2015/10/23/decision-soon-on-whether-trudeau-will-move-into-24-sussex-drive/wcm/72a30a5c-b286-4d15-8ba3-6cb9d3c1e4e4|title=Decision soon on whether Trudeau will move into 24 Sussex Drive|work=Toronto Sun|accessdate=2019-05-21|date=2015-10-23|last=Marquis|first=Melanie|language=en-CA}}</ref>。2008年，{{le|加拿大审计长|Auditor General of Canada}}在报告中估计需要花费1000万加币进行12到15个月的完全翻修<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.cbc.ca/canada/story/2008/05/06/ag-summary.html| title=Deportation failures, costly passports focus of AG's report| date=2008-05-06| work=CBC News| accessdate=2019-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026140220/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/story/2008/05/06/ag-summary.html|archive-date=2012-10-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。国家首都委员会正在制定大修计划<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ottawacitizen.com/news/local-news/ncc-seeks-advice-on-conserving-and-developing-official-residences|title=NCC working on plan to conserve 24 Sussex, other official residences|accessdate=2019-05-21|date=2015-09-10|last=Butler|first=Don|language=en}}</ref>，并估计需要约18个月施工时间<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/how-the-pms-residence-became-a-nightmare-at-24-sussex/|title=How the PM's residence became a nightmare at 24 Sussex| last=Kingston| first=Anne|date=2015-11-21|accessdate=2019-05-21|work=[[麦克林|麦克林]]}}</ref>。

也有人支持拆除并重建这栋房子<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.macleans.ca/uncategorized/its-time-to-tear-down-24-sussex/|title=It’s time to tear down 24 Sussex| last=Wells| first=Paul|date=2009-06-26|accessdate=2019-05-21|work=麦克林}}</ref>。

